  "brandStory": {
    "title": "Partnership Rooted in the Pacific",
    "description": "<p>Our journey began with a simple belief: that true beauty is born from the harmony between nature and the human hand. In the heart of the South Pacific, we've partnered with artisan cooperatives to bring you treasures that aren't just objects, but <strong>narratives of heritage</strong>.</p><p>Every coconut bowl is polished with local organic oil; every bag is woven with grass that has felt the tropical rain. By choosing EcoMafola, you are directly supporting village economies and ensuring that ancient skills thrive in a modern world.</p>",
